Queens Park Rangers are chasing West Ham midfielder Mohamed Diame.

Harry Redknapp's summer transfer plans are kicking into gear ahead of the Barclays Premier League kick-off.

And the QPR boss is interested in taking the midfielder to Loftus Road ahead of the new season.

