Diame has fallen down the pecking order at Upton Park with the arrival of fellow Senegalese Cheikhou Kouyate from Anderlecht.

Redknapp has already added Rio Ferdinand, Steven Caulker, Jordon Mutch and Mauricio Isla to his squad this summer.

Diame, 27, joined the Hammers from Wigan in 2012.

